title: Icosidodecadodecahedron
summary: In geometry, the icosidodecadodecahedron (or icosified dodecadodecahedron) is a nonconvex uniform polyhedron, indexed as U44. It has 44 faces (12 pentagons, 12 pentagrams and 20 hexagons), 120 edges and 60 vertices.[1]  Its vertex figure is a crossed quadrilateral.
